i (optional) before serving warm."}],"hintsAndTricks":["To make your own mayonnaise, please refer to <i>The Basic Cookbook<\/i>. Making your own mayonnaise will increase the total time of recipe."],"basicInfo":["easy","25m","30m","6 portions"]}